{"tid":1063578,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專家打亂電子再回復原狀　時光倒流有望成真？","createTime":"2019-03-16T01:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T06:07:35.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"806ac7183353981d62693d30188e46c87cf5e66a","tid":1063578,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T01:08:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2T9c1CW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2T9c1CW&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnAVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=b2c1ff36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2T9c1CW</a>"},{"pid":"782254a8ae49fd04a9c780c7e2b095c08d839bcc","tid":1063578,"uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T01:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190315/photo/bkn-20190315170001315-0315_00912_001_01p.jpg?20190315175542\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190315%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190315170001315-0315_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20190315175542&h=074211aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n科幻電影中常見的時光倒流情節，至今仍是人類的幻想。惟一個由俄羅斯等多國科家組成的團隊，早前挑戰熱力學第二定律「宇宙中一切都傾向衰變」的理論，在實驗室利用量子電腦，成功令打亂的電子位元自動回復到本來的狀態。雖然倒回的時間不足一秒，但已初步實現「時光倒流」。<br />\n<br />\n莫斯科物理科學與技術學院（MIPT）量子信息物理實驗室的首席研究員列紹域克（Gordey Lesovik），與美國及瑞士的研究人員，共同建立一個以「量子位元」（qubits）運作的電腦。量子位元是量子電腦中最小的資訊單位，由「1」和「0」或兩者混合組成，可儲存在電子上。 <br />\n<br />\n研究人員利用該電腦將一個電子打散，直至其動能消耗殆盡，他們在過程中計算及觀察到，電子可自動回復至10億分之一秒前的狀態。實驗發現，當電腦運作涵蓋2個量子位元時，電子復位的成功率高達85%，但若涵蓋3個量子位元，由於運算過程變得複雜，成功率會降至只有50%。<br />\n<br />\n不過列紹域克在研究報告中指出，除非是利用超級系統（supersystem）進行試驗，即是以量子電腦控制一切因素，否則在一般情況下，物體不太可能主動「倒流時光」。"},{"pid":"ebd6ad0f788e1087e2660ae6e27c75607cb03851","tid":1063578,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91ada415d91bf2cd5ce158279cb110e503aa281","tid":1063578,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T05:07:26.000Z","msg":"攪咁多野先得𠴱一秒都冇，咁不如搵民建聯搞至少爭取到多幾秒。"},{"pid":"94c2744ddb2935c46fb4659301427e67e59e97e8","tid":1063578,"uid":61416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T05:09:24.000Z","msg":"只想去為你 完成時光機器"},{"pid":"913660f37c0f6349191e2230081b17a27eab599f","tid":1063578,"uid":212246,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/marvelmovies/images/9/9f/Time_Stone-Clean.png/revision/latest?cb=20161118113541\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fmarvelmovies%2Fimages%2F9%2F9f%2FTime_Stone-Clean.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20161118113541&h=27f91e34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5f5932fc321467b6339fe482369671ada2cd5b8","tid":1063578,"uid":27530,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:14:00.000Z","msg":"我今日都叫我個仔執番好玩過既玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04d0b8614f8e3872431d7a0de82b16cef3d47a6","tid":1063578,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T07:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a18fda293ab58219cdca49a8b9516ec3e2dead8","tid":1063578,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T23:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4766a7c713b56a88356d6606a52e4a5a3a200f","tid":1063578,"uid":212493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T02:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係咁勁?"},{"pid":"f3521c0dbae589e2e560082ac90bc05aee84efb0","tid":1063578,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T02:39:34.000Z","msg":"又一超級英雄出現"},{"pid":"d104501745c36f39d996c64109ff18e2b8758409","tid":1063578,"uid":120123,"like":0,"disli